tp.pr5

Class Place

  • java.lang.Object
    • tp.pr5.Place
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PlaceInfo
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bunker, MockPlace, Trench

    public class Place
extends java.lang.Object
implements PlaceInfo
    It represents a place in the city.
    Places are connected by streets according to the 4 compass directions: North, East, South and West.
    Every place has a name and a textual description about itself. This description is displayed when the robot arrives at the place.
    A place can represent the spaceship where the robot is safe. When the robot arrives at this place, the robot shuts down and the application will finish.
    Author:
    Abel Serrano Juste
